data.title: Illinois Freemasonry 2014
data.meta_description: Illinois Freemasonry 2014 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document summarizes the spring 2014 issue of the Illinois Freemasonry magazine. It discusses membership in local Masonic groups and a recent Grand Lodge academic bowl tournament. It congratulates Jerry Yarrington on his 50-year Mason anniversary. It promotes an upcoming Grand Lodge golf outing and requests articles from local lodges about their activities and events.
